## Auth Akışı

```
Kullanıcı Email Girer
        │
        ▼
signUpWithEmail()          signInWithEmail()
        │                         │
        ▼                         │
createUserProfile()               │
(Firestore /users/{uid})          │
        │                         │
        └──────────┬──────────────┘
                   ▼
         onAuthStateChanged()
                   │
                   ▼
         useAuth() hook tetiklenir
                   │
                   ▼
         RootNavigator → HomeScreen
```

---

